data.title: Elan to acquire Athena Neurosciences in stock deal
data.meta_description: Irish drug delivery specialist Elan is to take over Athena Neurosciences in a stock swap worth $590 million. The takeover adds Athena's experience in drug discovery and biotechnology as well as strong marketing and distribution to neurologists to Elan.
